      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1276 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from one of the Imams (as) that He said:\n\"There is no shortening of the prayer for sailors on their ships, nor for the mule drivers (al-Mukari) and camel drivers (al-Jammal).\""
